WEBVTT

1
00:23:25.930 --> 00:23:29.400 
我们只有三十秒  立刻启动飞船
We've got 30 seconds. You need to fire engines now!

2
00:23:30.030 --> 00:23:32.120 
我想看一下他们在躲避什么
I'd like to see what they're running away from.

3
00:23:32.220 --> 00:23:34.300 
附近有我们的卫星吗
Do we have a satellite nearby?

4
00:23:39.810 --> 00:23:40.960 
放大
Enlarge.

5
00:23:45.210 --> 00:23:48.170 
你觉不觉得那小行星有点特别
Does that asteroid look unusual to you?

6
00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:49.720 
它的表面有许多疙瘩凸起
It looks lumpy.

7
00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:54.850 
要我说  它就像一块怀孕的石头
Hmm. I was going to say pregnant.

